	<article id="post-116" class="post-116 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-resources">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.pawm.ca/2011/12/alberta-surface-rights-board-srb-new-rules-kick-in-dec-01-2011/" rel="bookmark">Alberta Surface Rights Board (SRB): New rules kicked in Dec 01, 2010</a></h1>
			
